{"tid":256601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞幫紅磡毆劫男子　擸24條金及千萬日圓","createTime":"2017-05-24T15:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T01:08:30.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d09bd59b304a4677c78176caaf6fa2d982dc7472","tid":256601,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"紅磡發生劫金案，消息指，晚上近9時，一名男子報稱到都會道6號置富都會攞貨後，拿着一個中型手提篋，載着24條金條及1000萬日圓現金(約70萬港元)，準備離開。惟行至商場門口時，突有一名南亞漢趨近，搶奪其手提篋，男事主𡚒力反抗，與對方糾纏。 <br />\n<br />\n期間，再有2名南亞裔男子出現，各亮出一把摺刀指嚇事主，又向他拳打腳踢，事主寡不敵眾被搶走手提篋，賊人得手後迅速逃去。有目擊者指，事後看見約6至7名南亞裔男子，登上一輛客貨車離開。警員接報到場，用警車載事主在附近兜截，暫無發現。警方其後在東九龍及西九龍均設置路障，搜查賊蹤。案件現列行劫，正追緝6至7名南亞賊匪歸案，各人均戴口罩、穿黑色T恤及戴黑色Cap帽。"},{"pid":"d32330947994adb7e260481e7b9d3c8b18c0e875","tid":256601,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"走私金去日本嘅集團？<br />\n<br />\n黑吃黑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5c66426d9301fee90becdf0385fc6ccf798f0d","tid":256601,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵撚死啦走私賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52681bf7bdb1fcf7f74f8e1ebead993735c8f88","tid":256601,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:54:40.000Z","msg":"冇內皃我切"},{"pid":"08a09d1efd9a380b37c8bfdbabfaa2a176cdbe97","tid":256601,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d61782c75dce59429fcd609b0c44682029cddea","tid":256601,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"山口組vs南亞人"},{"pid":"54506d9be432362622712b4e84d644841c7dbee2","tid":256601,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"李偉文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2ae712cecba86115f7f994d37278517be0c483","tid":256601,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"南亞佬邊有咁多情報 有人放料收買南亞佬做野炸掛 南亞人不嬲好好人 一定係比人金錢利誘犯案"},{"pid":"89d5919f65388c5b68b9839835a178970de68a1f","tid":256601,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南亞佬邊有咁多情報 有人放料收買南亞佬做野炸掛 南亞人不嬲好好人 一定係比人金錢利誘犯案</blockquote><br />\n依家香港d黑社會搵晒南亞做打手啦<br />\n貪佢地命賤乜都夠膽死"},{"pid":"097b2faeb6fe2fa2a5fe5d2539c8680b04b8f9b9","tid":256601,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走私金去日本嘅集團？<br />\n<br />\n黑吃黑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯定啦,應該傾唔掂數,分唔均<br />\n搵南亞仔做最好<br />\n爛命一條,又難跟<br />\n認錢唔認人 而且又差唔多樣 鬼認到<br />\n你見好多人做野而家都唔請大圈仔同D老鼠<br />\n直接搵佢地 夠方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26f59abf3cfb171a859574002b867c415c53898","tid":256601,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T18:22:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae35c31539107d576e5440471b6637d9018172d3","tid":256601,"uid":36234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T20:03:49.000Z","msg":"成幾百萬喎總共"},{"pid":"6a436a61a28b325c9a5dd418bab90768a72623cb","tid":256601,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T20:27:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"807d66783b9168b311e2261e3fa07c7ab12655d2","tid":256601,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T20:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b306ff2dcb0a4b9469124d43a10bc95cd20f54","tid":256601,"uid":90038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"